Date: Mon, 30 Oct 2017 13:22:01 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] magma: implement 64-bit algorithm from GOST R 34.12-2015

64-bit algorithm (Magma) from GOST R 34.12-2015 is block algorithm from
GOST 28147 with fixed S-BOX and LE/BE changes. Implement Magma reusing
gost28147 implementation.

Signed-off-by: Dmitry Eremin-Solenikov <dbaryshkov@gmail.com>
